google_219.golden_query: SELECT CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN T2.label = '+' THEN T2.molecule_id ELSE NULL END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT T2.molecule_id) FROM atom AS T1 INNER JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id INNER JOIN bond AS T3 ON T2.molecule_id = T3.molecule_id WHERE T3.bond_type = '#'
sparksql_query: SELECT CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN m.label = '+' THEN m.molecule_id ELSE NULL END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT m.molecule_id) FROM atom a INNER JOIN molecule m ON a.molecule_id = m.molecule_id INNER JOIN bond b ON m.molecule_id = b.molecule_id WHERE b.bond_type = '#'

SELECT CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN T2.label = '+' THEN T2.molecule_id ELSE NULL END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT T2.molecule_id) AS percent FROM atom AS T1 INNER JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id INNER JOIN bond AS T3 ON T2.molecule_id = T3.molecule_id WHERE T3.bond_type = '#';

SELECT CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN T2.label = '+' THEN T1.molecule_id ELSE NULL END) AS FLOAT) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT T1.molecule_id) FROM bond AS T1 JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T1.bond_type = '#'
